# Technology Stack (v0)

*   **Frontend:** [Next.js](mdc:https:/nextjs.org) 15 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript
*   **UI:** [Tailwind CSS](mdc:https:/tailwindcss.com), [shadcn/ui](mdc:https:/ui.shadcn.com), Lucide Icons
*   **Backend API:** Node.js / [Express.js](mdc:https:/expressjs.com) (planned for Vercel Serverless Functions)
*   **Database (Primary):** PostgreSQL (via [Supabase](mdc:https:/supabase.com))
*   **Database (Vector Embeddings):** PostgreSQL with `pgvector` extension (via [Supabase](mdc:https:/supabase.com))
*   **Authentication:** [Supabase Auth](mdc:https:/supabase.com/auth)
*   **AI Model Interaction:** [Vercel AI SDK](mdc:https:/sdk.vercel.ai) (planned for embedding generation)
*   **Package Manager:** PNPM
*   **Deployment:** [Vercel](mdc:https:/vercel.com), [Supabase](mdc:https:/supabase.com)

